{"tid":2414675,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"《讀Hu時代》日本美學系列 之二《幽玄：薄明之森》廣東話書評｜書櫃裡的貓","createTime":"2021-02-19T14:54:39.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-21T08:16:10.000Z","uid":47910,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"690fbb403e82f7e05484900b53d0f30ba21727e3","tid":2414675,"uid":47910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T14:54:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V4fAV0e.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV4fAV0e.gif&h=f6fca5c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />Hello，各位巴絲，牛年快樂，身體健康<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n 我終於睇完《幽玄》 呢本書喇 可以寫返個書評<br />\n上一次講日本美學，都成個幾月前<br />\n如果大家上次有睇，今次都有返入黎，我會好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同上次一樣啦，呢一本書都係由 大西克禮教授寫嘅<br />\n一set三本入面嘅第二本<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果大家無睇到上一個po《物哀》嘅話，上一個po喺呢到：<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2340414/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2340414/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n想聽上一集呢，喺youtube / spotify / apple podcast到都可以聽返，阿lee吉多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nFacebook粉絲專頁：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/catsincabinet\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcatsincabinet&d=VW1JDW%2BJF%2FyRlCRofLrhGn0iZiuoirEQNng52NyFBY4%3D&h=0b215aad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/catsincabinet</a><br />\nYoutube到聽《讀Hu時代》：<a href=\"https://youtu.be/E9Hh2vpgQRY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FE9Hh2vpgQRY&d=VW1JDW%2BJF%2FyRlCRofLrhGn0iZiuoirEQNng52NyFBY4%3D&h=da842604\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/E9Hh2vpgQRY</a> <br />\nSpotify到聽《讀Hu時代》：<a href=\"https://open.spotify.com/show/3qh3sax15nxE0h6sz9aZT6?si=lzl-aFTlTI64GAzBDpj_FA&amp;nd=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fopen.spotify.com%2Fshow%2F3qh3sax15nxE0h6sz9aZT6%3Fsi%3Dlzl-aFTlTI64GAzBDpj_FA%26nd%3D1&d=VW1JDW%2BJF%2FyRlCRofLrhGn0iZiuoirEQNng52NyFBY4%3D&h=cb169bf4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://open.spotify.com/show/3qh3sax15nxE0h6sz9aZT6?si=lzl-aFTlTI64GAzBDpj_FA&amp;nd=1</a><br />\nApple Podcast到聽《讀Hu時代》：<a href=\"https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/%E8%AE%80hu%E6%99%82%E4%BB%A3/id1528292270\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpodcasts.apple.com%2Fus%2Fpodcast%2F%25E8%25AE%2580hu%25E6%2599%2582%25E4%25BB%25A3%2Fid1528292270&d=VW1JDW%2BJF%2FyRlCRofLrhGn0iZiuoirEQNng52NyFBY4%3D&h=373f074b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/%E8%AE%80hu%E6%99%82%E4%BB%A3/id1528292270</a><br />\n<br />\n事不宜遲，入正題喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">「幽玄」嘅七種意義</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">字義上嘅意義</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2RNLyRk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2RNLyRk.jpg&h=a8a92272&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「幽玄」就係有 掩藏、遮蔽、唔顯露、唔明確嘅意思<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但係幽玄當然唔係咁簡單啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">字義嘅衍生</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BhwTHMx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBhwTHMx.jpg&h=e429614b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n即係微暗、矇朧、薄明呢啲意思 <br />\n呢種幽暗，唔係令人恐懼不安嘅純黑，反而係溫柔、委婉嘅一種幽暗<br />\n姐係好似啲女明星咁<br />\n雖然成日話全裸演出<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，但永遠都會有啲陰影、杯、碟遮住啲重要部位<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無數次咁 呃撚咗當年清純嘅我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97f8ab6ebdc175174e888337c89401fa92069859","tid":2414675,"uid":47910,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T15:27:29.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">感官</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dEC7Nbk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdEC7Nbk.jpg&h=59a68f11&s={SIZE}\" />  <br />\n由第二階段延伸，就係想像黑暗之中嘅事物 <br />\n例如 就係伴隨著幽暗出現 寂靜 姐係好似個啲日本水著女星個啲片 或者 寫真咁樣 <br />\n個啲片唔會直接扑野，除曬啲衫 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢地會著啲水著，跟住同個camera好似拍拖咁樣 <br />\n會打下網球，會去沙灘玩下，喺酒店刷下牙，滴下啲牙膏係個大波波到<br />\n啲大波波又會fing黎fing去咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔會太過火，除曬衫嘅，但係只要你用下你嘅創作力量和幻想<br />\n可以FF下 有啲咩香味，啲肌膚嘅質感呀 <br />\n最後你就會「啊撕⋯⋯」咁樣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FP0Wcu6.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFP0Wcu6.gif&h=0a772316&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n相反，香港人就唔深明「幽玄之美」 <br />\n見到少少咸濕野，就會話：呢條女有無AV呀？有無seed呀？無seed？無番號？我屌你老母呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你懂不懂規舉呀？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢啲就唔深明「幽玄之美」 囉 <br />\n重要嘅唔係seed呀，重要嘅係你嘅想像力呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n補返原圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cWWo4X0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcWWo4X0.jpg&h=776b6c2f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<span class=\"x-small\"> <span class=\"pink\">^Key word 係篠崎 愛</span> </span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">「心」</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://stat.ameba.jp/user_images/20131201/23/taru-q-support/2b/8b/j/o0480064412767501241.jpg?caw=800\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstat.ameba.jp%2Fuser_images%2F20131201%2F23%2Ftaru-q-support%2F2b%2F8b%2Fj%2Fo0480064412767501241.jpg%3Fcaw%3D800&h=3daab4ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"x-small\"> ^上面係藤原定家，其中一位歌學大師 </span><br />\n喺和歌入面，古時侯嘅「歌人」或者「歌學大師」，就將和歌分成「心」、「詞」、「調」、「姿」 四個評核範疇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當中「心」就係指 一首和歌嘅 主題、內容、同埋核心思想 <br />\n「詞」就係遣詞，點樣表達個啲內容呢？ <br />\n「調」就係音調，點樣詠唱出黎？ <br />\n「姿」就係形式、甚至我會認為，係受眾接收嘅時候，所感受到嘅景物嘅姿態 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3298hZi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3298hZi.jpg&h=14ed1fe3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"x-small\">connect到美人嘅「心」，嗚哇</span><br />\n好似網絡上面流傳，有一個女人恭喜劉生，簽咗嘅一個叫 洪恩 嘅 蠢閪女人返去 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n恭喜人個個係乜水呢？可能係一啲姓李嘅美人黎掛？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係即使我地唔知 係邊個恭喜人，都無問題架喎 <br />\n因為佢想 屌柒啲負心漢 嘅「心」，毫無疑問咁 傳遞到俾我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地可以透過呢個「心」，了解到呢位女士嘅「姿態」，係幾咁嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而且呢個憤怒嘅「心」，係可以穿越千年，都可以感受得到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以，大西教授就會話，「幽玄」嘅深遠，唔止體現喺時間同空間上，連精神上，都可以we connect <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c268256aad1cadd4247bc66debeae1a9cabd525f","tid":2414675,"uid":47910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T15:46:23.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">「詞少而心深，鍛鍊龐雜之物」</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcQdpylk2kDSyBM0Naos3Xtkh-4fLKcdoSDOfw&amp;usqp=CAU\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fencrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com%2Fimages%3Fq%3Dtbn%3AANd9GcQdpylk2kDSyBM0Naos3Xtkh-4fLKcdoSDOfw%26usqp%3DCAU&h=9720663d&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n姐係小小嘅字數，內裏包含咗大大嘅資訊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好似和歌咁，格式就係五、七、五、七、七咁樣組成，總共有三十一個音節<br />\n你諗下，日本人講多謝，都要講「 a ri ga to u」 5個音 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁喺有限嘅音節之中，如果能夠傳達到好豐富嘅資訊俾讀者，就有一種「幽玄之美」 <br />\n就同第一至三嘅階段有啲似，表面上，作者可能寫咁啲好簡單嘅嘢，其實背後有著龐大而複雜嘅內容 包括 主題、思想、情緒、意境、世界觀等等<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">宗教意義</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.buddhistdoor.org/upload/file/20190418/33177/ab6b82fa2bc7ed434e7c0ca0d25d13fd_715__2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.buddhistdoor.org%2Fupload%2Ffile%2F20190418%2F33177%2Fab6b82fa2bc7ed434e7c0ca0d25d13fd_715__2.jpg&h=6bdb3fef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n本身「幽玄」就係宗教用詞，例如「佛法幽玄」<br />\n當中「幽玄」自然就帶有啲神秘，超自然性 甚至係形上學 嘅概念 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n特別係東洋美學 同 大自然 有住千絲萬縷嘅關係，而日本嘅神道教，就係 日本人 對於大自然嘅崇拜 <br />\n所以當 和歌 經常都借 大自然嘅景物，去表達 歌人 內心嘅感受嘅時候， 唔多唔少，都會滲入咗 對大自然嘅 敬拜之情 <br />\n當中，就可以feel到有啲宗教色彩喺入面喇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">不妨濛一點</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ENpugmt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FENpugmt.png&h=b7602194&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「幽玄」唔係一種單純嘅 隱秘<br />\n而係有一種 難以言喻嘅趣味，飄渺嘅氣氛，而日本人叫呢樣野做「餘情」 <br />\n大西教授甚至係講到，有一種「人與歌共同搖曳嘅情趣」 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n立即就令我諗起 Jazz入面嘅swing 爵士樂 <br />\n<img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/originals/87/9e/f7/879ef7139161917de4b30a7d53d2a5a8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.pinimg.com%2Foriginals%2F87%2F9e%2Ff7%2F879ef7139161917de4b30a7d53d2a5a8.jpg&h=0bd01ed8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔係單單好聽就會令人想起身，跟住un架嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果唔係，貝多芬、巴赫個啲你都可以un，但係你去啲orchestra 嘅音樂會，你唔會見到有人咁樣un<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地聽Jazz，佢個ensemble嘅arrangement 就係會令你想跟住fing <br />\n就好似有一種魔力，吸引你去跟住個音樂嘅節奏去搖擺<br />\n咁我覺得，呢種魔力，就好似大西教授所講嘅 個種難以解釋嘅「情趣」喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f79a519144e75d642fb931c72a35a88f1b6e6ef","tid":2414675,"uid":47910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T16:19:56.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">「幽玄」藝術作品</span></span></strong><br />\n上一次，大家都有問，到底有咩「物哀」嘅藝術品<br />\n所以今次我就決定喺到羅列幾個，等大家都可以親身體驗下<br />\n如果有多啲分享都可以留言喺下面講<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">能劇&amp;能面</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4v4xYG9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4v4xYG9.jpg&h=cb6be9f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"x-small\">第一次見到個面具，嚇到PK<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n面具之下嘅人，又係咪真係如同面具一樣呢？<br />\n舞台設計之中，亦有唔少黑暗嘅地方，呢啲故意留白嘅設計，係窮？定係留俾大家慢慢聯想呢？<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">漆器</span></span></strong><br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5Ws0n8P.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5Ws0n8P.jpg&h=7a6d12ff&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<span class=\"x-small\">好想食日本野，好肚餓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n除咗上面嘅植物，同入面嘅食物，漆黑嘅漆器，又會令大家聯想到啲咩呢？<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">三宅一生 - 陰翳 IN-EI</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cy2WFVt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCy2WFVt.jpg&h=4666a0d3&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cLSPgtO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcLSPgtO.jpg&h=dfa73e33&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n呢一批作品，非常完美咁表現出 日本人對於「光」「影」嘅獨特意識<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">安藤忠雄 - 光之教堂</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F6CzsAv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF6CzsAv.png&h=d31ceccc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"x-small\">安藤忠雄：若人生中追求「光」，首先要認真凝視眼前名為「影」的苦難現實</span><br />\n陰翳之中，十字架後嘅世界到底係點架呢？<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">黃偉文填俾JUNO嘅《濛》</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RgzNNsi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRgzNNsi.jpg&h=2ce14f01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n濛朧，曖昧嘅愛情，要是想纏綿 焦點係咪真係要鬆一點呢？<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">今敏 - 《千年女優》</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WbH7NAu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWbH7NAu.jpg&h=e3c39aa2&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n追逐幻想之中嘅愛人，完全演繹出「不妨濛一點」嘅愛慕之情<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">小津安二郎 - 《晚春》《秋刀魚之味》（含劇透）</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mVUmR19.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmVUmR19.jpg&h=e6479f97&s={SIZE}\" />  <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n兩套個核心主題其實係一撚樣嘅，但我會推薦《秋刀魚之味》多啲<br />\n因為 岩下志麻 後生真係好靚，好有氣質<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CsKRuRu.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCsKRuRu.gif&h=cfdd3833&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"x-small\">老實講原節子，真係her nose is too big<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n不過我唔多講啦，癈事下面又「你係咪鍾意鮑姐呀？」「鮑姐後生都好正」「鮑姐、鮑姐」咁洗我版<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/dllm.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後，你覺得幾正，可以subscribe我channel，我會定時up片，支持下我，多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e4be6b8397e0c6a06306bae5ebbf5d2f8773841","tid":2414675,"uid":11185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T17:13:35.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"758461b8d4f095025826f18708c3691de94d300b","tid":2414675,"uid":236359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e4be6b8397e0c6a06306bae5ebbf5d2f8773841","tid":2414675,"uid":11185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T17:13:35.000Z","msg":"留名"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T17:14:56.000Z","msg":"又撞到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nHi <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d1c1bb7d621869b641d92d26da188dde799f2b2","tid":2414675,"uid":59832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T17:20:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8626385ba3f68a7264f1a47da9292bf91e2153ca","tid":2414675,"uid":47910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T17:27:12.000Z","msg":"你地咁夜都唔訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 定喺外國？"},{"pid":"a46775799b1679dcf3ca84c2deb2897631502080","tid":2414675,"uid":236359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8626385ba3f68a7264f1a47da9292bf91e2153ca","tid":2414675,"uid":47910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T17:27:12.000Z","msg":"你地咁夜都唔訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 定喺外國？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T17:28:54.000Z","msg":"有無研究過日本電影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c0f6358f9824ff27e18ed2c4d2a362e9dfc1849","tid":2414675,"uid":47910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a46775799b1679dcf3ca84c2deb2897631502080","tid":2414675,"uid":236359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8626385ba3f68a7264f1a47da9292bf91e2153ca","tid":2414675,"uid":47910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T17:27:12.000Z","msg":"你地咁夜都唔訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 定喺外國？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T17:28:54.000Z","msg":"有無研究過日