,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a46775799b1679dcf3ca84c2deb2897631502080","tid":2414675,"uid":236359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T17:28:54.000Z","msg":"有無研究過日本電影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T17:30:16.000Z","msg":"Major本身讀media野<br />\n唔敢話研究，但都有睇嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/plan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T17:36:42.000Z","msg":"睇過咩導演戲？ 邊套最深刻？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T17:51:14.000Z","msg":"第一套令我開始睇得比較多日本電影 嘅電影，應該係大學film history堂嘅時候 睇黑澤明嘅《亂》<br />\n當時喺美國上堂，一睇 成個 hall嘅學生都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最有印象就係個art style ，個種濃烈嘅色彩 同 大場面嘅調度，真係好深刻<br />\n<br />\n當然，後來睇《七武士》同 橋本忍嘅 《複眼的影象》，我都認同橋本忍所講 《七武士》之後，黑澤明嘅電影 編劇方面 的確都偏向 自我滿足嘅<br />\n但大師就算退步，佢嘅 場面調度 真係令人五體投地<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e9ad59ad2b017cf4eea4d31cf567fee44cc77a7","tid":2414675,"uid":47910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d1756b4c9e2e6c194c0501c1ff7cee27a34301ce","tid":2414675,"uid":59832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8626385ba3f68a7264f1a47da9292bf91e2153ca","tid":2414675,"uid":47910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T17:27:12.000Z","msg":"你地咁夜都唔訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 定喺外國？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T17:46:39.000Z","msg":"sleep is for the weak<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T17:55:30.000Z","msg":"真，癈柴先訓教<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd9ab3083b4de4633ddc8255bbab07045ea9e4ae","tid":2414675,"uid":11185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"758461b8d4f095025826f18708c3691de94d300b","tid":2414675,"uid":236359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e4be6b8397e0c6a06306bae5ebbf5d2f8773841","tid":2414675,"uid":11185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor